LCD:
LCD RS pin to digital pin 12
LCD Enable pin to digital pin 11
LCD D4 pin to digital pin 5
LCD D5 pin to digital pin 4
LCD D6 pin to digital pin 3
LCD D7 pin to digital pin 2
LCD R/W pin to GND
LCD VSS pin to GND
LCD VCC pin to 5V
10k potentiometer to +5V and GND, with it's wiper (output) to LCD screens VO

Moisture sensor:
Connect the VCC pin of the sensor to the 5V pin of the Arduino.
Connect the GND pin of the sensor to the GND pin of the Arduino.
Connect the A0 pin of the sensor to the A0 (Analog) pin of Arduino.

Pump:
Pump (white) to centre
Pump (red) to USB (red)
USB (black) to upper
VCC to 5V, GND to GND
IN to A5
